data.description: Bring offers! Discover the epitome of exclusive waterfront living at a rare and unparalleled price point with this exceptional Dunedin waterfront townhome, boasting a coveted deeded boat slip right in your backyard. Located in the back of the community, on a quiet  cul- de-sac. Plenty of front & backyard greenspace for children & pets to play! Unleash your creativity with a clean slate awaiting your updates &  personal touch, presenting 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an expansive bonus room —a versatile space ideal for a home gym, office, or multigenerational living. Step into luxury as the foyer introduces a walkway leading to the bonus room, featuring tile floors, and a private patio overlooking your deeded 30 ft boat slip. The front & backyard offers plenty of green space for children & Pets to play! Seamlessly transition to the second floor, where a front living room with wood floors and vaulted ceilings awaits, accompanied by a patio offering southern views of greenspace. The kitchen, with a breakfast bar and dining room, opens to the great room, adorned with a wood-burning fireplace and soaring ceilings—creating an airy and inviting ambiance with water views from every angle! On the same floor, discover the second bedroom, a full bathroom, and a laundry closet.  Ascend the staircase to the third floor, where the primary bedroom and bath await in loft-style grandeur. Delight in the breathtaking views from your private patio, capturing the essence of the water and mesmerizing sunsets. Enjoy a lifestyle of ease with an HOA fee that covers water, sewer, trash, cable, internet, management, clubhouse access, pool and hot tub amenities, tennis courts, a gated boat dock, exterior maintenance, and even flood insurance. Remarkably affordable, this waterfront gem stands out, offering a rare opportunity for boat owners! Strategically located near Bayshore Blvd and the Pinellas Trail, this residence is 1/2 mile bike ride or walk to the Dunedin Causeway/Honeymoon Island and 1 mile to downtown Dunedin.  Revel in the vibrant atmosphere of a locale, named one of "The South's Best Beach Towns" by Southern Living Magazine for 2022. Also boasting Beautiful Caladesi & Honeymoon Islands! Indulge in the convenience of numerous restaurants, breweries, bars, grocers, and recreational activities—all within a short distance. With the added advantage of Curlew Landings allowing 3+ months leasing, and two pets, this complex offers a rare blend of versatility and luxury within an HOA. Don't miss the chance to claim your own slice of Florida paradise and make this extraordinary waterfront property yours!
